settings.title: Fall Floral Arranging Workshop
settings.title_2:
Workshop season is here and we kicked it off with our Fall Floral arranging class. We gathered together at our Studio City storefront with a fabulous group of creative ladies and spent a few hours learning about and playing with flowers. Flowers look great in a vase, but if you've got a little extra time at home these days and need a fun project, here are five great ways to play with your flowers!
